The paper deals with image forensic analysis, specifically the detection of double JPEG compression. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. Additionally, the paper involves the use of machine learning techniques, which could place it under the machine learning (cs.LG) category. The paper also deals with image compression and authenticity assessment, which could place it under the cryptography and security (cs.CR) and information retrieval (cs.IR) categories.
